We have specific users in our environment who are responsible for managing the templates in a given space, but who aren't space administrators.

There is currently no way to address this.

h5. Steps to reproduce
# Create a page with a title contains ampersand (ie. *&*). Let's say the page title is: _ABC & XYZ_
# Attach an image to the page
# Go to or create another page
# Display an image attached at _ABC & XYZ_ page with the following wiki markup:
{code}
!ABC & XYZ^imagename.jpg!
{code}
# The image will not be displayed after saving the Page and instead the following error message will appear:
{code}
Unable to render embedded object: File (imagename.jpg) not found.
{code}

A customer has reported that the following query takes up to 4 minutes to run on their database. 

{code:sql}
select page0_.CONTENTID as CONTENTID, page0_.CHILD_POSITION as CHILD_P13_, page0_.PARENTID as PARENTID, page0_.SPACEID as SPACEID,
       page0_.TITLE as TITLE, page0_.VERSION as VERSION, page0_.CREATOR as CREATOR, page0_.CREATIONDATE as CREATION6_,
       page0_.LASTMODIFIER as LASTMODI7_, page0_.LASTMODDATE as LASTMODD8_, page0_.VERSIONCOMMENT as VERSIONC9_, page0_.PREVVER as PREVVER,
       page0_.CONTENT_STATUS as CONTENT11_
from   CONTENT page0_
where  page0_.CONTENTTYPE='PAGE'
and    (
           (page0_.PREVVER is null ) and
           (page0_.CONTENT_STATUS='current' ) and
           (page0_.CONTENTID in (
               select distinct page1_.PREVVER
               from   CONTENT page1_
               where  page1_.CONTENTTYPE='PAGE'
               and    (
                          (lower(page1_.TITLE)='home' ) and
                          (page1_.PREVVER is not null ) and
                          (page1_.CONTENT_STATUS='current' )
                       )
               )
           ) and
           (exists(
               select space3_.SPACEKEY
               from   SPACEPERMISSIONS spacepermi2_, SPACES space3_, SPACES space4_
               where  spacepermi2_.SPACEID=space3_.SPACEID
               and    (
                          (spacepermi2_.PERMTYPE='VIEWSPACE' ) and
                          (lower(space4_.SPACEKEY)='xxxxxxxxxx' and page0_.SPACEID=space4_.SPACEID) and
                          (
                              (
                                  (spacepermi2_.PERMUSERNAME is null )and
                                  (spacepermi2_.PERMGROUPNAME is null )
                              )or(
                                   spacepermi2_.PERMUSERNAME='xxxxx' 
                              )or(
                                   spacepermi2_.PERMGROUPNAME in('xxxxx' , 'xxxxxx' , 'xxxxxx')
                              )
                          )
                      )
            )
       )
) limit 25;
{code}

This comes from the code:

{code}
public List<AbstractPage> getRenamedPagesInSpace()
    {
        if (space == null || title == null)
            return Collections.emptyList();

        if (possibleRenamesInSpace == null)
        {
            List<AbstractPage> redirects = pageManager.getPossibleRedirectsInSpace(space, title, 25);
            possibleRenamesInSpace = getPermittedEntitiesOf(redirects, 5);
        }

        return possibleRenamesInSpace;
    }
{code}

The explain for this query is:

{noformat}
mysql> explain select page0_.CONTENTID as CONTENTID, page0_.CHILD_POSITION as CHILD_P13_, page0_.PARENTID as PARENTID, page0_.SPACEID as SPACEID, page0_.TITLE as TITLE, page0_.VERSION as VERSION, page0_.CREATOR as CREATOR, page0_.CREATIONDATE as CREATION6_, page0_.LASTMODIFIER as LASTMODI7_, page0_.LASTMODDATE as LASTMODD8_, page0_.VERSIONCOMMENT as VERSIONC9_, page0_.PREVVER as PREVVER, page0_.CONTENT_STATUS as CONTENT11_ from CONTENT page0_ where page0_.CONTENTTYPE='PAGE' and ((page0_.PREVVER is null )and(page0_.CONTENT_STATUS='current' )and(page0_.CONTENTID in(select distinct page1_.PREVVER from CONTENT page1_ where page1_.CONTENTTYPE='PAGE' and ((lower(page1_.TITLE)='xxxxx' )and(page1_.PREVVER is not null )and(page1_.CONTENT_STATUS='current' ))))and(exists(select space3_.SPACEKEY from SPACEPERMISSIONS spacepermi2_, SPACES space3_, SPACES space4_ where spacepermi2_.SPACEID=space3_.SPACEID and ((spacepermi2_.PERMTYPE='VIEWSPACE' )and(lower(space4_.SPACEKEY)='xxxxx'  and page0_.SPACEID=space4_.SPACEID)and(((spacepermi2_.PERMUSERNAME is null )and(spacepermi2_.PERMGROUPNAME is null ))or(spacepermi2_.PERMUSERNAME='xxxxx' )or(spacepermi2_.PERMGROUPNAME in('xxxxx' , 'xxxxx' , 'xxxxx'))))))) limit 25;
